<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Andreas Voit von Rieneck, Amtmann zu Karlsburg und Karlstadt</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Rücksendung des Pferdes mit dem entsandten Boten, da sich er sowie Wiguläus und Wilhelm von Wolfstein sorgen, deswegen belangt zu werden.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_383" id="190v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_383_r1l18">Andres vot von Ryneck <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_383_r1l19">ʒu karlburg vnd karlſtat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_383_r1l20"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Andres als Jr vns nu ʒulecʒ <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt ſchıken wır nach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_383_r1l22">dem pfeͣrd / ſo wellet ır vns das ſenden etc / Alſo 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_383_r1l21">wan </ab></add> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_383_r1l23">
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ Jr </del> vnd ~ dıe vom wolfſtein beſorgen daʒ wır von <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_383_r1l24">angelangt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> möchten / ſo <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wır daʒ Jr vns <expan>daſſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> pfeͣrd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_383_r1l25">bey dıſem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchıket / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_383" id="190v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Andres Vot von Ryneck, <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu Karlburg und
                        Karlstat</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Andres, als ir uns nu
                                                zulecz <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt,
                                                schiken wir nach dem pfeͣrd, so wellet ir uns das
                                                senden etc., also <add>wan</add> wir und die vom
                                                Wolfstein besorgen, daz wir von
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> angelangt
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> möchten, so
                                                  <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir, daz ir uns
                                                  <expan>dass<ex>elb</ex></expan> pfeͣrd bey disem
                                                  <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> schiket.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
